'''娘子谷大屠殺'''是[[納粹黨|納粹黨]]在[[第二次世界大戰|第二次世界大戰]]進攻[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]期間，於[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]][[首都|首都]][[基輔|基輔]]附近山溝進行一系列[[大屠殺|大屠殺]]。

==過程==
最惡名昭著的屠殺事件發生在1941年9月29日-30日，33,771名猶太人在單一行動中被殺死。軍政府長官少將[[弗里德里克·埃伯哈特|弗里德里克·埃伯哈特]]，南方集團軍麾下的警察部隊總司令[[弗里德里希·耶克爾恩|弗里德里希·耶克爾恩]]和別動隊C隊司令[[奧托·拉斯徹|奧托·拉斯徹]]（Otto Rasch）決意要消滅基輔內全部的猶太人。[[特遣隊|特遣隊]]4A士兵、黨衛隊、[[親衛隊保安處|保安處]]、烏克蘭警方執行該次屠殺<ref name="Berkhoff-2">{{cite web | url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=hyYGOyX1IQUC&pg=PA303&dq=%22Ukrainian+sources+also+name+paramilitary+and+auxiliary+police+formations%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=lwQpUdaGH6PCigLKjIHYDA&ved=0CDEQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=%22Ukrainian%20sources%20also%20name%20paramilitary%20and%20auxiliary%20police%20formations%22&f=false | title=Babi Yar Massacre | work=Ibidem | date=May 28, 2008 | accessdate=February 23, 2013 | author=Karel C. Berkhoff | page=303 | format=Google book preview | isbn=0253001595 | archive-date=2015-02-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150218154851/http://books.google.ca/books?id=hyYGOyX1IQUC&pg=PA303&dq=%22Ukrainian+sources+also+name+paramilitary+and+auxiliary+police+formations%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=lwQpUdaGH6PCigLKjIHYDA&ved=0CDEQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=%22Ukrainian%20sources%20also%20name%20paramilitary%20and%20auxiliary%20police%20formations%22&f=false | dead-url=no }}</ref> 。娘子谷大屠殺是納粹政權進攻[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]期間最大的單一大屠殺<ref>{{cite book | title=The Wehrmacht: History, Myth, Reality | url=https://archive.org/details/wehrmachthistory00wett | author=Wolfram Wette | year=2006 | page=[https://archive.org/details/wehrmachthistory00wett/page/n134 112] |accessdate=2008-01-20 | publisher=Harvard University Press}}</ref>，只有1943年11月[[收缴行动|收缴行动]]（42,000-43,000人受害）的死亡人數更多<ref name="Lower">Wendy Morgan Lower, {{cite web |url=http://moses.creighton.edu/JRS/pdf/2007-18.pdf |title=From Berlin to Babi Yar. The Nazi War Against the Jews, 1941–1944 |accessdate=2014-04-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090305074504/http://moses.creighton.edu/JRS/pdf/2007-18.pdf |archivedate=2009-03-05 }} ''Journal of Religion & Society'', Volume 9 (2007). The Kripke Center, [[Towson_University|Towson University]]. I.S.S.N 1522–5658. Retrieved from Internet Archive, May 24, 2013.</ref>，[[1941年敖德薩大屠殺|1941年敖德薩大屠殺]]在1941年10月發生，當時[[羅馬尼亞|羅馬尼亞]]部隊殺死超過50,000名[[猶太人|猶太人]]<ref name="Browning">{{cite web | url=http://hampshirehigh.com/exchange2012/docs/BROWNING-Ordinary%20Men.%20Reserve%20Police%20Battalion%20101%20and%20the%20Final%20Solution%20in%20Poland%20(1992).pdf | title=Arrival in Poland | publisher=Penguin Books | work=Ordinary Men: Reserve Police Battalion 101 and the Final Solution in Poland | date=1992; 1998 | accessdate=May 24, 2013 | last=Browning | first=Christopher R. | author-link=Christopher Browning | pages=135–142 | format=PDF file, direct download 7.91 MB complete | quote=''Also:'' [http://www.webcitation.org/6GIJ2XpOy PDF cache archived by WebCite.] | archive-date=2013-10-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019043400/http://hampshirehigh.com/exchange2012/docs/BROWNING-Ordinary%20Men.%20Reserve%20Police%20Battalion%20101%20and%20the%20Final%20Solution%20in%20Poland%20(1992).pdf | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

娘子谷大屠殺遇難者包括數千名蘇聯戰俘、[[共產主義|共產主義]]者、[[吉普賽人|吉普賽人]]、[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]][[民族主義|民族主義]]者與平民<ref>[http://www.jpost.com/Jerusalem-Report/Jewish-World/A-Museum-for-Babi-Yar A Museum for Babi Yar] {{Wayback|url=http://www.jpost.com/Jerusalem-Report/Jewish-World/A-Museum-for-Babi-Yar |date=20130626000548 }}, [[The_Jerusalem_Post|The Jerusalem Post]] (23 October 2011)</ref>。根據估計，德國佔領期間總共有10萬至15萬人於娘子谷被殺<ref name="rpmag1">{{cite book|last=Magocsi|first=Paul Robert|title=A History of Ukraine|year=1996|publisher=University of Toronto Press|page=633|url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=t124cP06gg0C&printsec=frontcover&dq=A+History+of+Ukraine|isbn=978-0-8020-7820-9|access-date=2014-04-09|archive-date=2013-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130104031958/http://books.google.ca/books?id=t124cP06gg0C|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Borrero">{{cite book |url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=dhm0cGdrTOIC&pg=PA73&dq=Babi+Yar+150,000&hl=en&sa=X&ei=_49uUr6zBY_oiALhuICIDA&ved=0CDkQuwUwAQ#v=onepage&q=Babi%20Yar%20150%2C000&f=false |title=Russia: A Reference Guide from the Renaissance to the Present |publisher=Infobase Publishing |author=Mauricio Borrero |year=2009 |page=73 |isbn=0816074755 |format=Google Books preview |access-date=2014-04-09 |archive-date=2013-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031064404/http://books.google.ca/books?id=dhm0cGdrTOIC&pg=PA73&dq=Babi+Yar+150,000&hl=en&sa=X&ei=_49uUr6zBY_oiALhuICIDA&ved=0CDkQuwUwAQ#v=onepage&q=Babi%20Yar%20150%2C000&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===紀念館===
2016年9月29日，時任烏克蘭總統[[彼得·波罗申科|彼得·波罗申科]]與當地人士發起建立之娘子谷大屠殺紀念館落成啟用，該館位於[[基輔電視塔|基輔電視塔]]一側。[[2022年俄羅斯入侵烏克蘭|俄羅斯入侵烏克蘭]]期間，在2022年3月1日當地時間約下午五點許，[[基輔電視塔|基輔電視塔]]遭俄軍發射之兩枚導彈之攻擊波及受損<ref>{{cite news |date=2022-03-01 |title=breaking news |url=https://twitter.com/babynyarhmc/status/1498722192967843840 |work=娘子谷大屠殺紀念館twitter |accessdate=2022-03-01 |archive-date=2022-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220302000111/https://twitter.com/babynyarhmc/status/1498722192967843840 }}</ref>，唯原定攻擊目標的電視塔卻完好無損<ref name="as">{{cite news |url=https://en.as.com/en/2022/03/03/latest_news/1646324260_333367.html |title=WORLD NEWS: What is Babyn Yar? Why is it symbolic to Ukraine and Zelenskyy? |first=Andy |last=Hall |publisher=as.com |date=2022-03-03 |access-date=2022-04-01 |language=en |archive-date=2022-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220401164144/https://en.as.com/en/2022/03/03/latest_news/1646324260_333367.html }}</ref>。部分猶太團體公開聲明譴責俄軍之行為<ref>{{cite news |date=2022-03-01 |title=Jewish groups condemn a strike near the Babyn Yar Holocaust Memorial. |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2022/03/01/world/europe/kyiv-babyn-yar-holocaust-memorial.html |work=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]] |accessdate=2022-03-03 |archive-date=2022-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220302021526/https://www.nytimes.com/2022/03/01/world/europe/kyiv-babyn-yar-holocaust-memorial.html }}</ref>，及後BBC報道只有在旁邊尚未啟用的博物館大樓受襲損毁，主體建築與紀念碑等未受損<ref>{{cite news |date=2022-03-02 |title=Babyn Yar: Anger as Kyiv's Holocaust memorial is damaged |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-60588885 |work=[[BBC|BBC]] |accessdate=2022-03-03 |archive-date=2022-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220302214136/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-60588885 }}</ref>。

